articles.title: First Gen Z Indian-American In US Senate Race Raises Over $2,80,000 - NDTV
articles.description: Ashwin Ramaswami, the first Gen Z Indian-American running for a US State legislature, has raised over USD 280,000, which is considered to be a substantial figure at the state level.
articles.content:
Ashwin Ramaswami has raised a total of over USD 280,000 and has USD 208,000 cash on hand.
